      • testIsDigestAuthorizationHeaderFailure

        public void testIsDigestAuthorizationHeaderFailure()
        This test was designed to specifically test a try/catch that was added around base64 processing to ensure that we push out a more readable error condition when unsupported type is sent in. Specifically, this is testing the Digest which is closely related to NTLM but not supported in Waffle.
